備註 Remarks





基本素養 Basic Literacy
        無    

核心能力 Competence
■ 培養生物化學與分子生物學的專業知識
 
■ 學習其他生物醫學與生物技術相關領域知識
 
■ 培養閱讀與整理新知及表達研究成果的能力
 
□ 培養生物醫學各領域的知識技能與實驗設計能力與技能
 
□ 加強獨立從事研究能力
 
 

課程概述 Course Description
       課程之目標主要是幫助學生學習醫藥科學的發展與藥物設計 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
幫助學生學習醫藥科學的發展與藥物設計瞭解生物製藥監管，技術和質量生物製藥發展的深層思考

 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction for biopharmaceutical drugs design 2Discovery of biopharmaceutical drugs3Discovery of biopharmaceutical drugs4Development of biopharmaceutical drugs5Development of biopharmaceutical drugs6Manufacture of biopharmaceutical drugs7Manufacture of biopharmaceutical drugs8Global regulatory for clinical and commercial biologics drugs9Global regulatory for clinical and commercial biologics drugs10Quality requirements for clinical and commercial biologics drugs11Quality requirements for clinical and commercial biologics drugs12Pharmaceutical development: Quality by Design (QbD)13Pharmaceutical development: Quality by Design (QbD)14Pharmaceutical development: Quality by Design (QbD)15Pharmaceutical development: Design of Experiment (JMP)16Pharmaceutical development: Design of Experiment (JMP)17Pharmaceutical development: Design of Experiment (JMP)18Discussion 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


有關課程其他調查 Other Surveys of Courses
                   1.本課程是否規劃業界教師參與教學或演講?   是，約 6 次            
Is there any industry specialist invited in this course? How many times? Yes, about 6 times.
			
           2.本課程是否規劃內含校外實習 (並非參訪)?   否		   
Is there any in (out of) school practicum involved in this course? How many hours?  No




